import React from "react";
import { Grid, TextField, FormControlLabel, Checkbox, Container } from "@mui/material";

const Student_Register = () => {
  return (
    <>
    <Container>
      <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
          <TextField
            autoComplete="given-name"
            name="firstName"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="firstName"
            label="First Name"
            autoFocus
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6}>
          <TextField
            required
            fullWidth
            id="lastName"
            label="Last Name"
            name="lastName"
            autoComplete="family-name"
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <TextField
            required
            fullWidth
            id="email"
            label="Email Address"
            name="email"
            autoComplete="email"
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <TextField
            required
            fullWidth
            name="password"
            label="Password"
            type="password"
            id="password"
            autoComplete="new-password"
          />
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={12}>
          <FormControlLabel
            control={<Checkbox value="allowExtraEmails" color="primary" />}
            label="I want to receive inspiration, marketing promotions and updates via email."
          />
        </Grid>
      </Grid>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
};

export default Student_Register;
